From: Fennec Authors <patches@fennec.computer>
Date: Mon, 08 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] branding: register fennec://about WebUI page

Registers the fennec://about URL as a Chromium WebUI page. The page
is served as a bundled React page from the Vite build output (the same
pipeline as fennec://setup, fennec://newtab, etc.).

Content:
  - Fennec version and build date
  - Underlying Chromium version (for support purposes — not in the UA)
  - License breakdown: GPL-3.0 (Fennec) / BSD-3 (Chromium) / GPL-3 (uBO)
  - Link to fennec.computer
  - Link to the source repository
  - Open source attribution

The old chrome://settings/help page is still accessible but has been
rebranded to Fennec styling by the rename-chromium-to-fennec patch.

PILLAR: Branding / Transparency
JOURNAL: none

---
 chrome/browser/fennec/about_fennec_ui.cc         | 82 ++++++++++++++++
 chrome/browser/fennec/about_fennec_ui.h          | 35 +++++++
 chrome/browser/ui/webui/chrome_web_ui_controller_factory.cc | 4 ++++
 3 files changed, 121 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 chrome/browser/fennec/about_fennec_ui.cc
 create mode 100644 chrome/browser/fennec/about_fennec_ui.h

diff --git a/chrome/browser/fennec/about_fennec_ui.h b/chrome/browser/fennec/about_fennec_ui.h
